metadata.name: Oculus bacca
metadata.description:
Oculus bacca berry can be found in the deepest wilds of the dark forests. This berry consists of many eyeballs and poisonous whiskers. It mainly feeds on insects, but its venom can be deadly to humans. 

Do not touch or look into its eyes!

Nikita Shinov
NFT: 2000 × 2000 px
